title: 820-00165 U3210 Burnt
message:
Hi 
I got a 820-00165 Motherboard for No Power
U3210 was burnt badly from top So I replaced it also C3285 and C3286 had Liquid Damage, Both replaced. 
Still board is not powering up 
Missing PP5V_S4rS3 
PP3v3_S5 is 3.32V

Don't know where to start now

title: 820-00165 U3210 Burnt
message:
Check for any short on power rails of Thunderbolt area.

Trigger SMC_ONOFF_L and check for drop pulse at PM_PWRBTN_L at same time.
